entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The virus has been planted in the White Thranta network. Reimos will watch the data carefully and see if he can determine what it is they are really up to.
entries.journal_entry_description: Jabba thinks that the manager for the White Thranta Shipping Company, a front for Jabba's smuggling activities, is planning to break away from Jabba's control and take the company for his own. Jabba needs more information on the manager's plans. Reimos is a good slicer that has worked for Jabba before, but most of Jabba's people are known to the White Thranta staff. A fresh face can get into the company and insert a surveillance virus into the company's network. That fresh face just happens to be you. Plant the virus by using the Public Access Terminal inside the company.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Plant the surveillance virus in White Thranta Shipping's Public Access Terminal. You can find this terminal to the right as you enter the first room of the shipping company. The Public Access Terminal is on the opposite wall from the secretary.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Plant the Virus in the Public Access Terminal
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have inserted the surveillance virus successfully. Return to Reimos for your next job.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Good Work! You have completed the Digital Infection quest.
